>> source: https://feastandfarm.com/how-to-make-self-rising-cornmeal/
>> author: Feast and Farm
>> servings: 2 cups
>> total time: 5 minutes

Blend @cornmeal{1.75%cups (242 g)}, @all-purpose flour{6%Tbsp (45 g)}, @baking powder{2%Tbsp (24 g)}, and @salt{0.5%tsp (3 g)} together in a #bowl{}.

Use according to whatever recipe you are following.
